trans-unit.source: Provides data for any events that occur when a user clicks an image-based ASP.NET server control, such as the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputImage"></xref> or <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton"></xref> server controls.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder data for eventuelle hendelser som forekommer når brukeren klikker en bildebasert ASP.NET serverkontroll, som den <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputImage"> </xref> eller <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton"> </xref> serverkontroller.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: This class passes the location where a user clicked an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputImage> server control or an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen sender plasseringen der en bruker klikker en <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputImage>serverkontroll eller en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>Web serverkontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputImage>

trans-unit.source: Clicking an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputImage> server control causes a <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputImage.ServerClick> event to occur, while clicking an <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton> server control causes a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton.Click> event to occur.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du klikker en <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputImage>serverkontroll forårsaker en <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputImage.ServerClick>hendelsen oppstår mens du klikker en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>serverkontroll fører til at en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton.Click>hendelsen oppstår.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton.Click> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputImage.ServerClick> </xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlInputImage>

trans-unit.source: You can then use event handlers to programmatically respond to the event based on the value of these coordinates.
trans-unit.target: Du kan deretter bruke hendelsesbehandling programmatisk svarer til hendelsen basert på verdien for disse koordinater.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The origin coordinates (0,0) are located at the upper left corner of the image.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Kommer fra koordinatene (0,0) finnes øvre venstre hjørne på bildet.

trans-unit.source: Raising an event invokes the event handler through a delegate.
trans-unit.target: Opprettet en hendelse aktiverer hendelsesbehandlingen via en representant.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [NIB: Raising an Event](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/f2adaf01-1ed1-42e1-8c31-8d467e7e0ee2).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [NIB: opprettet en hendelse](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/f2adaf01-1ed1-42e1-8c31-8d467e7e0ee2).
